com.kuka.roboticsAPI.controllerModel.sunrise.connectionLib

Interface IMessageVisitor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ErrorMessageVisitor, FieldBusEventProvider, MessageVisitorAdapter, SunriseControllerStateTrackerImpl

    public interface IMessageVisitor
    Implemented by classes who need to react on Messages.
    See Also:
    Message.accept(IMessageVisitor)
    This element is an undocumented internal feature. It is not intended to be used by applications as it might change or be removed in future versions.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      static interface  IMessageVisitor.Context
      Context in which a visit takes place.

      Result of a message visiting operation Message.accept(IMessageVisitor).
